#### System information

Erigon version: `./erigon --version`

`erigon version 2021.10.3-alpha`

OS & Version: Windows/Linux/OSX

Commit hash : 5ca558c6670dd96afac472ef573152dda97fc866

#### Expected behaviour

RPC must send notification just one time about latest header as soon as it appears.

#### Actual behaviour

RPC sends two notifications about previous and new header.

#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour

1. Start Erigon and RPCDaemon in websocket mode
2. Subscribe to new headers. I will use `wscat`, you can use something else if you wish.

